Henri Debain https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henri_Debain 0 Henri Debain (3 August 1886 - 15 January 1983) was a French film actor. He first appeared in Le Petit café in 1919, and appeared in more than 25 films between 1919 and 1956. He directed three films including Mephisto in 1931. Henri_Debain ( 3_August_1886 - 15 January_1983 ) was a_French_film_actor . He first appeared in Le_Petit_café in 1919 , and appeared in more_than_25_films between 1919_and_1956 . He directed three_films including Mephisto in 1931 .
